{"tid":1341124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民意","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:31:42.000Z","uid":155919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1607fff5ba81e4d531fdcc682782ea45df912f01","tid":1341124,"uid":155919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:29:32.000Z","msg":"元朗今次真係失我民意<br />\n<br />\n成班羊群畀人趕上車任人打 仲要跪地求饒，真係無眼睇。<br />\n<br />\n你唔反擊，失去o既係想反擊，想勇武o既人o既民意。<br />\n你反擊，失去o既係一班本來就無心抗爭，充滿奴性o既人o既民意。<br />\n<br />\n咁鐘意做羊群你地做飽佢啦，動物係無權講自由民主架。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The tree of liberty must be refreshed from time to time with the blood of patriots and tyrants.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThomas Jefferson"},{"pid":"91a47375ec153585c0d4e3a9077a86e727098bf7","tid":1341124,"uid":232766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:30:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">六大訴求：</span></strong><br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 釋放被捕人士、撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會、並追究警隊濫權<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>追究元朗暴徒行兇、警察失蹤</strong></span>"},{"pid":"628c27a2a54fd3ce719e03c294d00d00a46b4a69","tid":1341124,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"黑警開槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n元朗鄉黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國網軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港政府失去合法性 進入無政府狀態</span></span>"}]}